<div id="challenges" class="demo-content mdl-color--white mdl-shadow--4dp content mdl-color-text--grey-800 mdl-cell mdl-cell--8-col">
  <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
    <h4>Activities</h4>
    Dolore ex deserunt aute fugiat aute nulla ea sunt aliqua nisi cupidatat eu. Nostrud in laboris labore nisi amet do dolor eu fugiat consectetur elit cillum esse. Pariatur occaecat nisi laboris tempor laboris eiusmod qui id Lorem esse commodo in. Exercitation aute dolore deserunt culpa consequat elit labore incididunt elit anim.
    <ul class="demo-list-icon mdl-list">
      <% activities.each do |activity| %>
        <% activity.challenges.each do |challenge| %>
          <%= link_to not_alone_activity_path(category: activity.id, challenge: challenge.id),
                      class: "mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect mdl-button--accent animated-link" do %>
            <li class="mdl-list__item" id="activity_<%= activity.id %>_challenge_<%= challenge.id %>">
              <span class="mdl-list__item-primary-content">
                <div class="js-emojione" style="width: 18px;">
                  :<%= challenge.icon %>:
                </div>
                <%= challenge.text %>
              </span>
            </li>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
